  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A continental breakfast is served each morning with fresh pastries made by the chef pâtissier, seasonal fruits, freshly baked breads as well as a vast selection of teas and coffee. Those opting for half board can enjoy dinner in L Dolce Vita restaurant with waiter service. Guests can choose a starter and main from the menu and there is also a salad buffet. Wine, beer and soft drinks are included with half board plus. </p>
<p><strong>La Dolce Vita restaurant </strong>is located in the hotel's original Belle Époque style lounges. Here you'll be treated to unforgettable culinary experiences. Indulge in the gourmet cuisine served by the chef, using organic local ingredients from the Batani Farm. During summer the restaurant moves out to the elegant terrace to dine beneath the stars. The resident sommelier will assist you in selecting the perfect wine to accompany your meal. </p>
<p><span><strong>La Dolce Vita al Mare</strong> beach side bar offers the possibility to be served from the comfort of your beach side sun lounger. The restaurant offers a lunchtime buffet service which includes choices of fresh salads, fish, meat, desserts and fruit. </span></p>]]></cateringDescription>
