  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Pool &amp; Beach</strong></span></p>
<p>The hotel has a large swimming pool surrounded by sun loungers. The pool is normally open from May to September.</p>
<p>There's also a beach service from around 23 May to 12 September (weather dependent). If you upgrade to half board plus this service is included free of charge and you can choose sunbeds on the beach between row three and seven. </p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Spa</strong></span></p>
<p>Enjoy exclusive rejuvenating spa treatments in the tranquil atmosphere of the Dolce Vita Spa. Relax in the Turkish bath, Finnish sauna, rem showers or Jacuzzi. The spa is payable locally (approx. €25 per person per day). </p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Free use of bikes (subject to availability)</li>
<li>Fitness Room</li>
<li>Parking (payable locally approx. €18 per day)</li>
<li>Free WiFi</li>
<li>24 hour reception </li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
