  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>This is one of the most elegant hotels in Rimini. Its grand liberty style building stands out on the beachfront promenade and the interiors are impressive. We love the ball room where you can eat dinner at La Dolce Vita restaurant. It's a real treat in the summer when it opens out onto the terrace and lawn. There's a great outdoor pool, a beach club (payable locally) and a spa with indoor heated pool (payable locally).</p>]]></listingDescription>
