  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Executive Rooms </strong>reflect the liberty style of the historic building with original parquet flooring and antique furnishings. They're about 20m² with a comfortable king sized bed, Sky TV, minibar, safe, air conditioning and electric blinds. These rooms sleep two people. Executive rooms with a side sea view are available for a supplement and on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms </strong>are about 20m² and have a comfortable king sized bed or twin beds. These rooms sleep up to three people.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
